# Workflow Checklist (auto-generated)

- [x] P00 PRECHECK - preflight passed
- [x] P10 PROVISION - pod created or provisioning skipped by policy
- [x] P20 TARGET_BIND - LIUM target or fallback host resolved
- [x] P30 POD_READY - pod status and remote reachability validated
- [x] P40 BOOTSTRAP - prereqs/helpers completed
- [x] P50 CHECKOUT - repo, python env, and data contracts satisfied
- [x] P60 SWEEP - sweep launched or skipped by policy
- [x] P70 MONITOR - sweep status validation completed
- [x] P80 FETCH - requested artifact fetch completed or skipped
- [x] P90 TEARDOWN - keep/delete policy applied
- [x] P99 SUMMARY - final flow verdict emitted

